<!-- wp:heading {"level":3,"className":""} -->
<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="h-3-they-design-for-flow-and-function-not-just-looks">3. <strong>They Design for Flow and Function, Not Just Looks</strong></h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"className":""} -->
<p>Flashy is nice, but smart beats shiny.<a href="https://www.ncaa.org/sports/2016/2/10/coaches.aspx"> NCAA programs</a> obsess over layout for their sports locker room. They create a <strong>functional flow</strong> so players can move, store gear, and prep without chaos.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"className":""} -->
<p>A few practical tips I've learned on the job:</p>
